{"tid":650602,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京 箱根 河口湖自駕遊一問","createTime":"2018-05-02T13:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T14:24:49.000Z","uid":106976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5bad780bbe0997add5104923c61f1c8b5719c0","tid":650602,"uid":106976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"黎緊六月會去6日東京 打算頭兩日係東京市內<br />\n第三日朝早會去箱根 <br />\n打算stay 2日2夜 <br />\n第5日去橫濱玩一日一夜<br />\n之後渣車番成田番香港<br />\n<br />\n暫時<br />\nDay 1 0900 -1500 到成田拎車  東京市內<br />\nDay 2東京市內<br />\nDay 3 渣車去箱根 玩箱根 訓箱根<br />\nDay 4 河口湖 午 御殿場 晚箱根<br />\nDay 5 去橫濱 訓橫濱<br />\nDay 6 番東京 補貨 晏就4點機<br />\n<br />\n想問 箱根 河口湖依啲玩唔玩到咁耐？<br />\n會去大涌谷 御殿場依啲"},{"pid":"3c949d76722d77d18b70969286e70dfa120db0d5","tid":650602,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c2929dfd2e13fd94c42fa892edc9bf4d5ff536a","tid":650602,"uid":100904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"河口湖都夠玩成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938486e4d061d59320969171a088218240864865","tid":650602,"uid":106976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c949d76722d77d18b70969286e70dfa120db0d5","tid":650602,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"係係預中午買到佢收工🤤"},{"pid":"aa7ab02d5596b987a6e452ed29eda387b28b885b","tid":650602,"uid":175896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"未去過橫濱但睇你行程提議你不如今次玩多D河口湖同富士山周邊先 都好多野睇既<br />\n橫演留下次<br />\n另外御殿場都真係可以行大半日 同埋你自駕的話 排入去停車場都預返9個字1個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個叫忍野八海既 可以唔使去 好伏"},{"pid":"e3749146d1ef1f7f767d93c12ba78d7b54b43d34","tid":650602,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"河口湖一帶都幾多野可以去喎